OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Flate evening sunshine to end the day.
OL,7,FLargely clear skies overnight, though
OL,8,Flow cloud and mist returning to the
OL,9,FPennines. A mild night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAnother fine, dry and very
OL,12,Fwarm day. Any morning low cloud and
OL,13,Fmist once again quickly clearing to
OL,14,Fleave prolonged periods of strong
OL,15,Fsunshine throughout Thursday. Calm
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
